---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Centricle"
  description="Privacy Policy for Centricle products and services."
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10"><em>Last updated: February 28, 2026</em></p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">

        <p class="text-slate-300">
          This policy covers centricle.com, the portfolio website of Kevin Smith / Centricle LLC, based in Ocean Pines, Maryland. Individual products (mileweave.us, whoami.fyi, etc.) maintain their own privacy policies specific to their data practices.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">What this site does</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          centricle.com is a personal portfolio. It showcases projects, provides a contact form, and links to individual product sites. It does not require accounts, collect passwords, or store personal data in a database.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Information we collect</h2>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-200">Contact form</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          When you submit the contact form, your name, email address, and message are processed by Netlify Forms and delivered to us via email. We use this information only to respond to your inquiry. We do not add you to any mailing list.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-200">Analytics</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand how visitors find and use this site. GA4 collects anonymized usage data including pages visited, traffic sources, and general location (country/region). Google Analytics uses cookies. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Google's privacy policy</a> for details on how Google processes this data.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-200">Server logs</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Our hosting provider (Netlify) automatically collects standard server log information including IP addresses, browser type, and pages visited. These logs are managed by Netlify per their <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">privacy policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Third-party services</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm text-slate-300">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-700 text-left">
                <th class="py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-slate-200">Service</th>
                <th class="py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-slate-200">Purpose</th>
                <th class="py-2 font-semibold text-slate-200">Privacy Policy</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50">
                <td class="py-2 pr-4">Netlify</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4">Hosting, form processing</td>
                <td class="py-2"><a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Link</a></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-700/50">
                <td class="py-2 pr-4">Google Analytics</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4">Usage analytics</td>
                <td class="py-2"><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Link</a></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          This site uses cookies only through Google Analytics. No first-party cookies are set. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Data retention</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Contact form submissions are retained only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry. Analytics data is retained per Google's default retention settings (14 months).
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          You may request deletion of any personal data we hold (primarily contact form submissions) by <a href="/#contact" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">contacting us</a>. We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Children’s privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Questions about this policy? <a href="/#contact" class="text-teal-400 hover:underline">Get in touch</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
